{"type": "article", "id": 11991, "title": "Lanvin 新香水", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-13T11:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000158ac9T8JYxWK0smIwv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tLanvin 最近推出新香水，名为 “Eyes On You”，瓶身设计和 Eclat d’Arpege 一脉相承，Alber Elbaz 给看起来甜蜜蜜的瓶身画上了一个妩媚又搞笑的表情。香水前调是西西里岛柠檬和丁香，中调是绿茶和桃花，基调是黎巴嫩雪松和白麝香，目前有 50 毫升和 100 毫升两种规格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000157J0KBrwdC731QelGa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060001571baPqSrM8D6jZYk2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}